{"tid":748183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺朗豪坊跌咗八達通","createTime":"2018-07-19T04:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T05:19:24.000Z","uid":164979,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"229db73b677ab480ae9125c6eee4035b614ac893","tid":748183,"uid":164979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"唔該我想問吓呢到有冇人今朝係朗豪坊執到張八達通？<br />\n<br />\n我應該係今朝大約0850係朗豪坊間M記買完野食，搭電梯落返地下，再上戲院睇早場呢段路嘅中途跌咗。<br />\n<br />\n之前我係喺旺角C出口出，再轉上去M記，唔排除都有可能係呢段路跌咗<br />\n<br />\n張八達通係個人八達通嚟，有個藍色gundam 00嘅八達通套<br />\n<br />\n如果有人執到嘅話麻煩通知一聲。感激不盡。THX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e593f561fd0d6540905911a723486a4d44a0490","tid":748183,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"傻的嗎，個人八達通直接打2266 2266報失啦。<br />\n仲有買M記都用八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9528e34ac0520c4917c54db2c0974befa78eba02","tid":748183,"uid":26675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"Gundam 00<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c954c9d2c0e56f28064981636d8abeaf5da1a452","tid":748183,"uid":164979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e593f561fd0d6540905911a723486a4d44a0490","tid":748183,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"傻的嗎，個人八達通直接打2266 2266報失啦。<br />\n仲有買M記都用八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"個八達通套都用咗幾耐吓，有啲感情<br />\nBtw我買M記係用現金，可能係我扮野入袋個陣跌咗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過唔該曬你幫手推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee3296576609f38360bd5be2a3b37de997cd66a","tid":748183,"uid":19712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"大叫 gundam!"},{"pid":"a1b94c9492f01f00b01cc6d6d6778096cd2482e3","tid":74818